Would you ever walk into your home and fill it with garbage? Probably not. It is completely mind-boggling to me that whilst we have respect for our homes, a lot of people take their imprint on the planet we live on for granted by adding to the never ending problem of plastic polution. It's time to start thinking about the Planet and your effect on it. Not only for yourself, but for your children.
